\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Would you tell me your full name?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 My full name? My own name. Elizabeth Selkirk Kidd, oh - Hay my married name. You don't need to write all that in here do you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 And your address at the moment is Balmwell House?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 What year were you married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 1914. The eleventh of August.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 What year were you born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 1890. Third of February.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Where about were you born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 137 St Leonard's Street. As long as I hear what you're saying to me dear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 How many years did you live in the house where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Oh - perhaps until I was about ten.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 So that would just be to the turn of the century?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Where did you go to when you left there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 To Parkside Street, seventeen. That's still St Leonard you know. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Can you remember why you moved?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 A bigger house. There was eleven of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 How long did you stay at Parkside Street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Oh well, perhaps about the same I think dear. And then we went over to Kirkway Side. Thirty-four.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Why did you go to Causeway Side, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 I don't know dear. No. No. Probably a better house, I don't know dear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Were you there until you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Were there quite a while. And then we shifted again to 5, Lord Russell Place. Further down.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Round about when was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Oh, perhaps two years before I was married. 1911 or 1912.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 And you can't remember exactly why you moved?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 No. No. It would be - bigger house likely you see. It would be that dear, or a better house, you know, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 You said there was eleven of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Uh huh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Can you tell me, starting with the oldest one, their names and how much there was between them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Yes, I've a good idea, two years between each one. Yes. Uh huh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Can you start with the eldest one and tell me their names?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Well the first one of course died, I didn't know - him but - then there was my sister Janet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Can you remember what year the first one was born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Oh I've no idea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Janet, and then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Janet. William. John. Elizabeth. Uh huh. Susan. Mary. Alan. Margaret, and of course the first one was Margaret. Uh huh. Margaret and -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Did she die very young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 
Mm. Oh yes, just a baby. Baby with whooping cough - I remember that, I've been told it, mother tell me it you know. How many is that dear?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Nine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Nine. Sandy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 One more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Can't remember the other, oh it does}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13922216\charrsid10619451  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 nae matter. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Do you know how old your father was when you were born? Was he a young man or was he getting on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 He would be middle age I would think dear. Oh he'd be a young man I would say. I wouldn't know dear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Where did he come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Rosalyn.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 What was his job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 He was a timekeeper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Where about was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 In Causeway Side. A builder contractors. A timekeeper, kept the time of the men you know what they work. That's what he -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Was that always his job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Or did he have another one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Did he ever work part time as well as that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 No. No dear, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Do you ever remember your father being out of work at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 No, I don't dear, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Can you remember roughly how old your mother was when you were born?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 No idea.
