\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Yes, all rented houses dear.
