\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 So you don't know what he was like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 No. No.
