Round about Sloan Street, the district of Pilrig, round about there, who were considered the most important people who lived round about there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Oh I don't know dear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Nobody thought that anybody was anymore important than anybody else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Your husband was a shopkeeper, was he regarded as important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Yes, and he was very well known you know. Everybody knew the Hays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 What about teachers or ministers, doctors?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Well nothing like that round about where we were. No, not - not in Sloan Street anyway.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 What sort of people went to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Mm, a lot of fine people. They all lived in the south side, up this way you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Was it just ordinary people who went to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Oh all kinds dear, mixed, just like any - oh yes, of course, all kinds. Business folk and working folk dear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Would you say that the working folk, the other people all had the same standard of living?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Well there is a difference dear isn't there now, with the working people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 At that time there was was there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Oh yes. A big difference.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 What sort of people would you call working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Ourselves like, we're working class, shop folk and we -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 You said there was a difference between some people, what other sort of people were different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Well maybe doctors and ministers, you've got to look up to them haven't you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 And their families you would say were different from your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Yes. Uh huh. There is a big difference. You're maybe just as good mind dear, we're just as good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Do you think that they felt different from you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Yes I do. Uh huh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 You think they felt superior in some ways?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Yes. Well some was - more snobs than anything else dear. The real kind don't do that dear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Were some families thought of as rough and some respectable?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Uh huh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 What sort of jobs would the father have, the husband, if he was a rough type person?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 What - what kind -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 What sort of job would he have if he was a sort of rough type of person?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Oh well a labourer - on the roads or that you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 And respectable would be shopkeepers and so on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Oh yes. Oh yes. Mm hm.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Was there any difference between a craftsman and a labourer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 No, I don't think it dear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 You never had a struggle to make ends meet did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Never. Never dear in my life, I've never wanted for anything.
