\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11233132 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 So Georgina was about the middle of the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16139654 EH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15729822\charrsid10619451 Yes, uh huh. She was eight.
